Class ListenerPublisher

java.lang.Object
org.eso.ias.plugin.publisher.PublisherBase
org.eso.ias.plugin.publisher.impl.ListenerPublisher
All Implemented Interfaces:
MonitorPointSender
public class ListenerPublisher extends PublisherBase
ListenerPublisher is an implementation of MonitorPointSender for testing the BufferedPublisherBase: monitor points are sent to the listener.
Author:
acaproni
